Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.88,0:10:46.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.02,0:10:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个使用破魔之箭\N叫做戈薇的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:10:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒你想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有毒虫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.08,0:11:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别乱来啊  弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.62,0:11:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你连毒蜂也吸进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.63,0:11:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  你去追珊瑚还有戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.30,0:11:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  弥勒  你别死喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想逃吗
